| Aspect | Unit Tests (templates.rs, share_render.rs) | Integration Tests (gateway/tests) |
|--------|---------|----------|
| Location | `#[cfg(test)]` module at end of src/*.rs | Separate crates/gateway/tests/*.rs files |
| Dependencies | Mock data, no AppState needed | Full GatewayState + services + server |
| Scope | Helper functions, serialization, HTML output | Full HTTP server with auth middleware |
| Setup | Create test data structs directly | Start full server on ephemeral port |
| Testing | Call functions directly with inputs | Make actual HTTP requests to server |

### Test File Locations Summary

```
/Users/penso/.superset/worktrees/moltis/tailscale-redirects/
├── crates/web/src/templates.rs (lines 763-811) - 4 unit tests
├── crates/web/src/share_render.rs (lines 575-901) - 9 unit tests
└── crates/gateway/tests/
    ├── auth_middleware.rs (integration tests for auth/routing)
    └── chat_ui.rs (integration tests for WebSocket handshake)
```

There is **no separate tests/ directory** in crates/web - all tests are inline with `#[cfg(test)]` modules.

